 Mother takes t=\r\nime and is not a painless process unlike that of the baby.\n&gt; &gt;That results =\r\nin the problem that &quot;real=C2=A0surges&quot; of energy may=C2=A0result=C2=A0in me=\r\nntal havoc.=C2=A0\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt;Secondly, many people who have Kundalini rise =\r\nare brought up with the concept of japa. Japa which deals with the Air elem=\r\nent which is unstable anyway can cause serious instability in these people.=\r\n\n&gt; &gt;Some=C2=A0of the=C2=A0people who have Kundalini &quot;rises&quot; may be people w=\r\nho may feel that they haven&#39;t done a single worthwhile thing in their lives=\r\n and think that the faking of Kundalini rises may help them get some esteem=\r\n in the eye of the general public.=C2=A0\n&gt; &gt;Coming to the specific problem:=\r\nIn general, for any doctor, the separation of the true from the false claim=\r\ns must precede any attempt at helping the patient. A true Kundalini rise ne=\r\neds niyama to finish Vata. Vata tends to like irregularity, in food habits,=\r\n sleeping habits, sexual matters, travel.=C2=A0\n&gt; &gt;To finish Vata, all=C2=\r\n=A0that must be regimentalised, then appropriate herbs used. Control of Apa=\r\nna is essential as is Bramhacharya. Application of oils to the body to tota=\r\nlly calm Vata may be useful. I suppose even Shiro basti in difficult real c=\r\nases may be useful.\n&gt; &gt;Then institute small=C2=A0Homas to MahaGanapati and =\r\nthe nava grahas to be performed by the patient. That should really improve =\r\nmatters, as Ganesha is The Lord of the Muladhara.\n&gt; &gt;The whole process may =\r\nbe chalked out over one-two years.\n&gt; &gt;In pure non real cases, just psychoth=\r\nerapy may be sufficient.\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt;Jai Shree Rama\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt;Jai Shree=\r\n Rama\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt;On Friday, March 1, 2013, Narasimha P.V.R. Rao  wrote:\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt;=\r\nNamaste friends,\n&gt; &gt;&gt;=C2=A0\n&gt; &gt;&gt