rms of Kundalini and its rise. Just do sadhana, =\r\novercome your\n&gt;  weaknesses and improve your detachment over time. Again, I=\r\n want to emphasize that detachment is not disgust or distaste for life/thin=\r\ngs/people around you. Disgust is the other side of coin of attachment. It i=\r\ns a negative attachment.\n&gt; &gt;&gt;=C2=A0\n&gt; &gt;&gt;\n&gt; &gt;&gt;Don&#39;t worry about \n&gt; whether y=\r\nour Kundalini rises or not. Worry about whether you are able to resist 6 in=\r\nternal enemies (shadripus) and 8 bondages (ashta pashas) or \n&gt; not. If your=\r\n ability to resist them is increasing, you are making progress. EVEN IF you=\r\nr Kundalini is fast asleep, you are still making progress. When you complet=\r\nely overcome them, Kundalini (your self-awareness) \n&gt; will automatically as=\r\ncend to the top and meet Her Lord (true Self).\n&gt; &gt;&gt;=C2=A0\n&gt; &gt;&gt;*=C2=A0=C2=A0=\r\n=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0 *=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0 =\r\n*\n&gt; &gt;&gt;=C2=A0\n&gt; &gt;&gt;One word on surrendering to a personal deity. Though true =\r\nsurrender is helpful, most people do not have it. They simply do business w=\r\nith god. Though people may be offended by my words, this is the plain and b=\r\nare fact.\n&gt; &gt;&gt;=C2=A0\n&gt; &gt;&gt;&quot;I want X, I will pray to you and please give it t=\r\no me&quot;, &quot;I am scared of Kundalini rise, I will pray to you and please protec=\r\nt me&quot; - all this is just a business deal. There is something you want and y=\r\nou ask god for it. True surrender has no place for agendas, desires, demand=\r\ns or expectations. True surrender is losing oneself in one&#39;s fascination fo=\r\nr the qualities of Lord. True surrender is accepting anything Lord throws o=\r\nne&#39;s way (whether it is pleasurable or highly painful) as Lord&#39;s prasad and=\r\n accepting it gratefully. True surrender is thinking of Lord with fascinati=\r\non and pleasure, even in the face of (and dur